            {
                "s2_paper_id": "188e5bbffd6e08670daa94b8c2779c2a2f585baa",
                "title": "The symplectic Verlinde algebras and string K\u2010theory",
                "year": 2009,
                "venue": "",
                "citation_count": 4,
                "reference_count": 27,
                "abstract": "We construct string topology operations in twisted K\u2010theory. We study the examples given by symplectic Grassmannians, computing K*\u03c4(L\u210dP\u2113) in detail. Via the work of Freed\u2013Hopkins\u2013Teleman, these computations are related to completions of the Verlinde algebras of Sp(n). We compute these completions, and other relevant information about the Verlinde algebras. We also identify the completions with the twisted K\u2010theory of the Gruher\u2013Salvatore pro\u2010spectra. Further comments on the field\u2010theoretic nature of these constructions are made.",
